Kane Kosugi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kane_Kosugi 0 Kane Kosugi (ケイン・コスギ, Kein Kosugi, born October 11, 1974, in Los Angeles, California), is an American martial artist and martial arts actor of direct Japanese and Chinese descent. His middle name Takeshi (健) is also his Japanese name (Kosugi Takeshi (小杉 健)). He is the son of martial arts film star Sho Kosugi. In Japan, Kane is considered gaijin tarento (foreign talent) due to his Nisei (second generation) foreign born heritage.
